quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  41,1,"Haa, miim."
  41,2,"Ko jipporiinde immorde ka Jurmetee…óo, Hinnotoo…óo on."
  41,3,"Deftere fensitaande aayeeje mum, janngeteende e …óemngal aarabu, wonan,de yim…ďe anndoo…ďe."
  41,4,"wewlinaynde jeertinaa…ďe. Kono …ďur…ďe …óuu…óude …ďen e ma…ď…ďe, …óuurnii, …ďeen …ďe nanataa."
  41,5,"∆Āe mb'i: ""∆Āer…óe amen no ommbanii ko noddataa men e mum kon, noto hino e noppi amen, heedo kadi hino hakkunde amen e maa. Haray wonu e golle maa ; menen kadi mi…óen e golle amen""."
  41,6,"Maaku: ""nganndee ko ne…ó…óanke yeruujo mon. Wahayinaama e am, won'de Dewetee…óo mon on, ko Dewetee…óo gooto. √Ďii…ďee e …óum, insinano…óon mo"". Bone woodanii sirkoo…ďe …ďen."
  41,7,"…ďe njonnataa …ďeen askal, hara kadi hi…ďe njeddi fii La'akara."
  41,8,"Pellet, …ďeen gooŇč…óiin…ďe …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īi …óin, hino woodani …ďe njo…ďdi ndi ta∆īondirtaa."
  41,9,"Maaku: ""Eey mon on njedda oon tak…óo leydi ndin ndeer bal…óe …ói…ói, mba…óanon mo goree…ďe? Awa ko oon woni Jey…óo winndere ndeen."
  41,10,"O wa…ói pelle e dow mayri, O hebbini barki e mayri, O e…ď…ďi nguureeji mayri …óin e ndeer bal…óe nayi timmu…óe, wonan'de lamndotoo…ďe …ďeen."
  41,11,"Refti o fotondiri ka kammu, fewndo ka ngu curkinnoo, O daalidani ngun kanngu e leydi ndin: ""ngrdiree …óoftaare, maa karheede"". ∆äi wi'idi: ""Min ngarii ko min …óoftii …ďe""."
  41,12,"O timminiri …ói kammuuji jee…ói…ói ndeer bal…óe …ói…ói, O yamiri kala kammu, fiyaaku maggu. Min cu…óiniri kammu aduna ngun, koode e reenir…óum. ∆äum ko e…ď…ďoore poolu…óo, ganndu…óo On."
  41,13,"Si …ďe …óuurnike, haray wi'u …ďe: ""Min nejertinirii on haacaangu, sugu ha'acaango Aadi'en e Samuuda'en."
  41,14,"nde Nulaa…ďe …ďren ardirannoo…ďe, ye'eso ma…ď…ďe e …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, won'de: ""Wata on ndewu dey, si wonaa Allah"", …ďe mb'i: ""Si Joomi amen haajuno, ko Malaa'ika O jippinaynoo. Awa minen, ko min yeddu…ďe ko nula…óon mum kon""."
  41,15,"Aadii'en kan, …ďe mawnintini ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, …ďe mbi'i: ""Hara ko hommbo …ďuri min doole?"" E …ďee yiaani, won'de Allah tak…óo …ďe On no …ďuri …ďe tii…óude doole? ∆Āe ngoni e yeddugol Aayeeje amen …óen."
  41,16,"Min ngurti henndu …ďuu…ďundu e ma…ď…ďe e √Īalaa…óe hiitaa…óe, fii no Min mee…óinira …ďe lepte koyeera …óen ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet, ko lepte La'akara …óen …ďuri won'de koyeera, kadi …ďe faaboytaake."
  41,17,"Samuuda'en kan, Min …ďannginanno …ďe; kono …ďe su…ďii bum…óam …óam e dow peewal ngal. Dillere lepte hoynooje …óen nanngiri …ďe, sabu ko …ďe paggitotonoo kon."
  41,18,"Min nda…óndi gooŇč…óim…ďe …ďe woniina hulnoo…ďe …ďen."
  41,19,"√Ďalnde noon ay√Ī…ďe Allah …ďeen moo…ďiroytee faade ka Yiite... Hara he…ďe √Īo∆ī∆īindiree."
  41,20,"Haa si …ďe hewtii nge, nann…óe ma…ď…ďe …óeen, e gii…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, e guri …ďalli ma…ď…ďe …óin seeditoo e dow ma…ď…ďe, kon ko …ďe gollatnoo."
  41,21,"∆Āe wi'ana guri ma…ď…ďe …óen: ""Ko fii honl…óum seeditani…óon e amin?"" ∆äe wi'a: ""Ko Allah wowlin…óo kala hu'unde On, wowlini men. Ko KaŇčko tagunoo on gila ka laawol aranol, ko ka makko kadi ruttete…óon""."
  41,22,"On ngonaani hi…óon cuu…óora, fii wata nan…óe mon, e gii…óe mon, e guri mon seedito e mon. Kono on cikkuno, won'de Allah anndaa ko …óuu…ói e ko ngolloton."
  41,23,"Ko …óuum moo…óon, cikkuno…óon Joomi mon, …óuum halki on. Wa…ótin…óon jeyyaa…ďe e pertu…ďe …ďeen."
  41,24,"Hay si …ďe mu√Ī√Īike, ko Yiite ngen wonata jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe; si …ďe …óa…ď…ďii feleede ngaccitee, …ďe wonaani feletee…ďe accitee."
  41,25,"Min ngurtani …ďe wondii…ďe, …ďeen cu…óinani …ďe ko woni ye'eso ma…ď…ďe, e ko woni …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe. Konngol [lepte] ngol jojji e ma…ď…ďe, won'dude e mofte yawtunoo…óe ado ma…ď…ďe, immorde e jinna e yim…ďe. Pellet, …ďe laatino hayru…ďe."
  41,26,"Yeddu…ďe …ďeen mb'i: ""Wota on jentito ndee Alqur'aanaare, sonkee e mayre (tuma nde janngetee) mbelajo'o, on foolay""."
  41,27,"Ma Min mee…óiniroy yeddu…ďe …ďeen, lepte sa…ótu…óe, Min njo…ďira ko …ďuri bon'de e ko …ďe ngollatnoo noo kon."
  41,28,"Ko …óum woni njo…ďdi a√Ī…ďe Allah …ďeen: Ko Yiite ngen. Ko galle luttugol woodani …ďe ton, njo…ďdi kon ko …ďe yeddiraynoo aayeeje amen …óen."
  41,29,"Yeddu…ďe …ďen mbi'a: ""Joomi amen, hollii min majjinnoo…ďe min …ďeen ka jinna e ka yim…ďe, min yaa…ďa …ďe min fuga, haa …ďe wona e …ďur…ďe joltude …ďen""."
  41,30,"Pellet, wi'u…ďe …ďeen : ""Joomi amen ko Allah"", refti …ďe tabiti; Malaa'ika'en hino jippoo e ma…ď…ďe (wiide): ""Wota on hulu, wota on suno; wewliree Aljanna, on mo wonano…óon fodeede."
  41,31,"Ko minen ngoni ni walloo…ďe on …ďeen ka nguurndam aduna e ka La'akara. Hino woodani on ton, kala ko woŇčkiiji mon woo…óetee, hino woodani ton, kala ko noddoton,"
  41,32,"ko maraari, immorde e kaforoore, Hinnotoo…óo""."
  41,33,"Hara ko hommbo …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude konngol, wano on noddu…óo e fii Allah, o golli mo∆ī∆īere, o wi'i: ""miin, ko e juul…ďe …ďen mi njiyaa?""."
  41,34,"Mo∆ī∆īere ndeen fotataa e bone on. Du√Īir (golle bon…óe …óen) kon ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude; e jaka yoo, on mo ngayngu woni hakkunde maa e mum, himo wa'ita wa gi…óo sa…ótu…óo giggol."
  41,35,"Kono hawrataa e …óuum, si wonaa mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďen; hawrataa e …óuum, si wonaa jom ge…óal mawnungal."
  41,36,"Si sowinsinoore arii he…ďude ma immorde e seytaane, moolor Allah. KaŇčko ko O Nanoowo, ganndu…óo."
  41,37,"Hino jiyaa e Ma'andeeji makko …óin, jemma on e √Īalawma on, e na'ange ngen e lewru ndun. Wota on cujjan na'ange ngen wonaa kadi lewru ndun. Cujjanee Allah, tak…óo …ói On, si wonii ko KaŇčko ndewoton."
  41,38,"Si …ďe townitike, …ďeen won…ďe ka Joomi maa kan, hi…ďe cubbunhinorana mo jemma e √Īalawma, hara …ďe haa…ďataa."
  41,39,"Hino jeyaa e Ma'andeeji makko …óin, tawde a nji'ay leydi ndin no yoori. Si wonii Min njippinii ndiyam to…ďo e mayri, ndi dilla ndi fontoo. Awa nguurnitu…óo ndi on, pellet, ko wuurnitoowo maay…ďe …ďen, tawde pellet, ko O kattan…óo haka hu'unde."
  41,40,"Pellet, oo√Īotoo…ďe …ďeen e aayeeje Amen …óeen, …ďe vuu…óotaako Min. E ko feroytee…óo on ka Yiite …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude kaa ko aroyoowo on √Ďalnde Darngal hino hoolii? NGollee ko paala…óon, ko pellet, Homo reeni ko ngolloton kon."
  41,41,"Yeddu…ďe …ďeen Alqur'aana tuma nde arnoo e ma…ď…ďe, pellet noon, ko nde deftere teddunde [foolnde];"
  41,42,"mehre iwrantaa nde ye'eso mayre, wonaa …ďaawo mayre. Ko jipporiinde immorde ka √Ďee√Īo, jettinii…óo On."
  41,43,"A wi'aaka si wonaa ko Nulaa…ďe adinoo…ďe ma …ďen mbi'anoo. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko O Jom yaafuyee, e Jom lepte mu'usuu…óe."
  41,44,"Si Min mba…óuno nde janngeteende e haala ajami, …ďe wi'atno: ""Ko ha…óno aayeeje mayre …óen fensitee? E nde wonat e haala ajami, [Nulaa…óo] on wona aarabuujo?"" Maaku: ""Kayre wonan'de gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen, ko nde peewal e cellal"". ∆Āe ngooŇč…óinaa …ďen kan, noto hino e noppi ma…ď…ďe …óin, kayre ko nde ni…ďe e dow ma…ď…ďe; …ďen hino noddiree e nokku wo…ó…óu…óo."
  41,45,"GooŇč…óii Min ngokkii Muusaa Deftere ndeen, nde luutondira e mayre. Si wonaano Konngol ardinoongol immorde ka Joomi maa, hakkunde ma…ď…ďe √Īaaweteno. Kam…ďe kan, pellet, hi…ďe e sikke sikkitii…óo nde."
  41,46,"Kala gollu…óo ko mo∆ī∆īi, ko fii hoore-makko; kala kadi bonnu…óo, yantat e makko. Joomi maa ciforaani won'de, too√Īoowo jiyaa…ďe …ďen."
  41,47,"Ko ka makko woni ko ganndal Darngal nduttetee. Dim…óe yaltataa e coom…ói mum, deyel (woo) saawataa,ngel jibintaa si wanaa e ganndal makko.√Ďande O noddiroyta …ďe:""Ko honto woni kafidaa…ói am …óin?"", …ďe mbi'a:""Min nganndinii Ma, alah e amen seedotoo…óo […óum]"""
  41,48,"∆Āe majjira e ko ko …ďe ndewatnoo ko adii; …ďe yananee won'de da…óirgal alanaa …ďe."
  41,49,"Ne…ó…óaŇčke on kaa…ďataa toragol mo∆ī∆īere. Si bone memii mo, ko o ta∆īotoo…óo, jonndinii…óo."
  41,50,"Si Min mee…óinir mo mo∆ī∆īere immorde ka Amen, …ďaawo nde lorra memi mo, ko pellet o wi'ay: ""∆äuum …óoo ko min ! Mi pellitaani si Darnga daroto. Si mi nduttaama ka Joomi am, ko pellet, mo∆ī∆īere hino woodani lam ka makko"". Ma Min kumpitu yeddu…ďe …ďeen, fii ko …ďe huuwi kon, ko ma Min mee…óinoy …ďe lepte sa…ótu…óe."
  41,51,"Si Min neeminii e ne…ó…óaŇčke on, o …óuurnoo o toowna balaaje makko; si bone non he…ďii mo, o wona jom toraare jaaynde."
  41,52,"Maaku: ""Yeetee kam, si wonii le ko ka Allah nde iwri, refti njeddu…óon nde; haray ko hommbo …ďuri majjude on gon…óo e lurral wo…ó…óungal?"""
  41,53,"Aray Min kolla …ďe Ma'andeeji Amen …óin ka tatteeji e ma…ď…ďe tigi, haa …ďanngana …ďe won'de ko nde goonga. E yonaani won'de Joomi maa, ko O ceedii…óo kala hu'unde?"
  41,54,"Ganndee he…ďe e cikke fii hawroygol e Joomi ma…ď…ďe. Ganndee non, ko O hu…ďindii…óo kala hu'unde."
